\begin_body

\begin_layout Title
用generalized parton distributions阐释重子结构
\end_layout

\begin_layout Author
Thomas Young
\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
Abstract
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
generalized parton distributions ，大约在十年(1995)之前被引入。
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "ref1"
literal "false"

\end_inset

成为用来描述强子的通用工具——使用夸克和胶子自由度。它结合了 form factors, parton densities and distribution
 amplitudes——以前在很长时间的函数内被用来研究强子结构的函数。GPD 类似于非相对论量子力学中的 Wigner quasi-probability
 函数，后者编码了一个量子力学系统的所有信息。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
GPD的最终目的是提供一个核子的三维空间图像，以及夸克轨道角动量和各种各样的 inter- and multi- parton correlation
 的直接测量.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
补充：单举与遍举
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset CommandInset href
LatexCommand href
name "What's the difference between inclusive and exclusive decays?"
target "https://physics.stackexchange.com/questions/1217/whats-the-difference-between-inclusive-and-exclusive-decays#"
literal "true"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
实验解释An experimental take
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Exclusive
\series default
 意味着你测量了所有产物的能量和动量（下文会有一个例外）
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Inclusive
\series default
 意思是你可能有一些产物不进行测量。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这对散射过程和衰变过程都适用。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Some things to note:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Exclusive measurements 允许你 nail down(确定，明确；用钉钉住) 一个良好定义的物理过程，而inclusive
 measurements 会告诉你一个过程的某个collection。If there are more than a couple of products,
 就会需要很多实验仪器，方能可靠地把他们全部收集起来，并估计实验完成度。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在你所提问的过程中，中微子必然是观测不到的，致使这个实验是 inclusive，更进一步的说，常常用 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{X}$
\end_inset

 来指代末态中未测量或者未指明的 stuff（也就是说实验一开始就设计成 inclusive ）。这里未指明的情况包括，in high acceptance
 instruments，你考虑带有特定产物的所有事件：其中一些 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{X}$
\end_inset

 为空，其中一些 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{X}$
\end_inset

 不为空而且well characterized, 还有一些 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{X}$
\end_inset

 ill-characterized。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Theoretical view
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
我不是很确定理论学家如何使用这些术语，但是应该是类似的。比如: 
\series bold
exclusive 
\series default
意思是单个过程，
\series bold
inclusive 
\series default
指的是所有过程包括所有详细产物。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Convergence of theory and experiment
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
当然，除非我们理论结合实验，否则我们学不到任何东西。但是这个过程可能很traumatic(痛苦的；极不愉快的) for both communities。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
不过，exclusive 测量和计算很清楚地指的是同一个事情，而 inclusivity 可以达成一致，with some care in building
 the experiment and assembling the theoretical results.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Experimenters cheating on exclusivity
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
有的时候，在核物理学中，我们把一些散射实验当成 exclusive，但是有一些重的，反冲的原子核没有测量。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这里的假设是，它仅仅携带了能动量中的一小部分，可以被忽略。然而可能会有些风险，如果这个原子核最后是处于高激发态的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In particular my dissertation(专题论文;学位论文) project was on 
\begin_inset Formula $A(e,e^{\prime}p)$
\end_inset

 reaction (elastic scattering of protons out of a stationary nuclear target
 where the beam was characterized and both the proton and outgoing electron
 were observed),and we assumed that the remnant(残余部份；剩余部份) nucleus was left
 largely undisturbed and recoiling with a momentum opposite the Fermi motion
 of the target proton.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
preface
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
文章内容介绍
\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
揭开物质的层次：从原子到 partons
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
量子力学可观测量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于一个纯态，密度矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

定义为，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\rho\left(\vec{r}_{1},\vec{r}_{2}\right)=\psi^{\ast}\left(\vec{r}_{1}\right)\psi\left(\vec{r}_{2}\right)
\]

\end_inset

测量了
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

就可以知道量子系统的所有信息。 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
补充
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
H & =\sum_{q}p\dot{q}-L(q,\dot{q})\\
p & =\frac{\partial L}{\partial\dot{q}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
约定
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{\mu\nu}=g^{\mu\nu}=\text{diag}(1,-1,-1,-1)
\]

\end_inset

逆变张量和协变张量分别为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v^{\mu}=(v_{0},\vec{v}),\quad v_{\mu}=(v_{0},-\vec{v})
\]

\end_inset

全反对称 Levi-Civita 张量 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

，采用归一化
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varepsilon^{0123}=1,\quad\varepsilon_{0123}=-1
\]

\end_inset

这个归一化有一个subtle 的负号，因为
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

要求指标
\begin_inset Formula $\mu\nu\rho\sigma$
\end_inset

各不相同，所以四个指标同时升降的时候，一定会有个负号(
\begin_inset Formula $3$
\end_inset

负号
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

正号)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
它遵守 Schouten 恒等式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g^{\alpha\beta}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}-g^{\alpha\mu}\varepsilon^{\beta\nu\rho\sigma}+g^{\alpha\nu}\varepsilon^{\beta\mu\rho\sigma}-g^{\alpha\rho}\varepsilon^{\beta\mu\nu\sigma}+g^{\alpha\sigma}\varepsilon^{\beta\mu\nu\rho}=0
\]

\end_inset

这个恒等式来自于四维空间中不存在五阶完全反对称张量。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这个公式的证明如下，
\begin_inset Formula $\mu\nu\rho\sigma$
\end_inset

各不相同，穷尽四维空间的指标个数。不失一般性的，设
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=\mu,\beta=\nu$
\end_inset

，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & g^{\alpha\beta}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}-g^{\alpha\mu}\varepsilon^{\beta\nu\rho\sigma}+g^{\alpha\nu}\varepsilon^{\beta\mu\rho\sigma}-g^{\alpha\rho}\varepsilon^{\beta\mu\nu\sigma}+g^{\alpha\sigma}\varepsilon^{\beta\mu\nu\rho}\\
 & =g^{\alpha\beta}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}+g^{\alpha\nu}\varepsilon^{\beta\mu\rho\sigma}\\
 & =g^{\alpha\nu}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}+g^{\alpha\nu}\varepsilon^{\nu\mu\rho\sigma}=0
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其他情形类似，一共有
\begin_inset Formula $4$
\end_inset

种情况，把它们加起来即可（并考虑奇偶置换带来的符号）。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Clifford 代数的表示
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
狄拉克矩阵遵守四维 Clifford 代数
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\{ \gamma^{\mu},\gamma^{\nu}\right\} =2g^{\mu\nu}\cdot\mathbbm{1}_{4\times4}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbbm{1}_{4\times4}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $4\times4$
\end_inset

的单位矩阵。我们主要使用两种特殊表示。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Weyl 表示
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在这个表示中，一个双旋量包括一个左Weyl旋量
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}$
\end_inset

和右Weyl旋量
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{\uparrow}$
\end_inset

，只需要把它们放在一起即可构建。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\lambda_{\uparrow}\\
\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

这就是 Dirac 旋量。这么做的主要原因是，在空间宇称变换下，这两个Weyl 旋量会交换位置，
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}\leftrightarrow\lambda_{\uparrow}$
\end_inset

。回忆洛伦兹群的表示
\begin_inset Formula $L_{+}^{\uparrow}=SO(3,1)=SO(4,\mathbb{C})_{\downarrow R}\approx\left(SL(2,\mathbb{C})\otimes SL(2,\mathbb{C})\right)_{\downarrow R}$
\end_inset

——a real form of the complexified group of four-dimensional rotations。由一对数字
\begin_inset Formula $\left(j_{1},j_{2}\right)$
\end_inset

标记，它们是
\begin_inset Formula $SL(2)$
\end_inset

群Casimir 算子 
\begin_inset Formula $J_{i}^{2}$
\end_inset

的本征值
\begin_inset Formula $j_{i}(j_{i}+1)$
\end_inset

。旋量
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{\uparrow}$
\end_inset

分别按照
\begin_inset Formula $(\frac{1}{2},0)$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $(0,\frac{1}{2})$
\end_inset

表示变换。
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}$
\end_inset

的共轭(complex conjugate)变换形式像
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{\uparrow}$
\end_inset

，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{\chi}_{\downarrow}^{\ast}\sim i\sigma^{y}\lambda_{\uparrow}
\]

\end_inset

其中第二个泡利矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{y}$
\end_inset

作为电荷共轭矩阵。Dirac 矩阵在 Weyl 表象下的形式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma^{\mu}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & \bar{\sigma}^{\mu}\\
\sigma^{\mu} & 0
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma^{\mu}=(1,\vec{\sigma}),\quad\bar{\sigma}^{\mu}=(1,-\vec{\sigma})
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[\sigma^{i},\sigma^{j}\right]=2i\varepsilon^{ijk}\sigma^{k},\quad\left\{ \sigma^{i},\sigma^{j}\right\} =2\delta^{ij}
\]

\end_inset

相应的手征矩阵和电荷共轭矩阵的形式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma^{5}=i\gamma^{0}\gamma^{1}\gamma^{2}\gamma^{3}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & 0\\
0 & -1
\end{array}\right),\quad C=i\gamma^{2}\gamma^{0}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
-i\sigma^{2} & 0\\
0 & i\sigma^{2}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma^{5}=\frac{i}{4!}\varepsilon_{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\sigma}=-\frac{i}{4!}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\mu}\gamma_{\nu}\gamma_{\rho}\gamma_{\sigma}
\]

\end_inset

手征矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

的要点在于，
\series bold
它要与所有的其他
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

矩阵反对易
\series default
。
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \gamma^{5},\gamma^{\mu}\right\} =0,\left\{ \gamma^{5},\sigma^{\mu\nu}\right\} =0$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
电荷共轭矩阵具有表象无关的关系
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C^{T}=C^{-1}=-C,\quad C^{2}=-1,\quad C\gamma^{\mu}=-(\gamma^{\mu})^{T}C
\]

\end_inset

电荷共轭矩阵可以用来做转置
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
C\gamma_{\mu}^{T}C=\gamma_{\mu},\quad C\gamma_{5}^{T}C=-\gamma_{5},\quad C\left(\gamma_{\mu}\gamma_{5}\right)^{T}C=-\gamma_{\mu}\gamma_{5},\quad C\sigma_{\mu\nu}^{T}C=\sigma_{\mu\nu}\label{eq:A.12}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{\mu\nu}=\frac{i}{2}\left[\gamma_{\mu},\gamma_{\nu}\right]$
\end_inset

是反对称矩阵，它具有性质
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\gamma^{5}\sigma^{\mu\nu}=\frac{i}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\rho\sigma}\label{eq:A.13-1}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

三个
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

矩阵乘积可以被约化成一个，通过等式
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}=g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{\rho}+g^{\nu\rho}\gamma^{\mu}-g^{\rho\mu}\gamma^{\nu}+i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma^{5}\label{eq:A-13}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这个等式实际上蕴含着一个重要的思想，把张量按照对称性进行分解。也就是说，
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
如果
\begin_inset Formula $\mu\nu\rho$
\end_inset

全相等，结果为
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
如果有两个相等，可能性为
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{\rho}+g^{\nu\rho}\gamma^{\mu}-g^{\rho\mu}\gamma^{\nu}$
\end_inset

，这里其实和全部相等有重叠，如果全部相等，刚好回到
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}$
\end_inset

，所以上面的一项可以去掉。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
三个指标各不相等，这样的话，我们考虑引入另一个矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\sigma}$
\end_inset

,且
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma\notin\{\mu,\nu,\rho\}$
\end_inset

，利用
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}=i\gamma^{0}\gamma^{1}\gamma^{2}\gamma^{3}$
\end_inset

，和
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}=-\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\mu},\mu\neq\nu$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}\gamma_{\mu}=1,\text{ without sum }\mu$
\end_inset

，这种对称性下的项可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma^{5}(-i\gamma_{\sigma})=i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma^{5}
\]

\end_inset

注意到由于
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

的全反对称性质，
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

只取
\begin_inset Formula $0,1,2,3$
\end_inset

中的一个值，与取全部值（求和）是等价的，因为我们假设了
\begin_inset Formula $\mu,\nu,\rho$
\end_inset

各不相等，穷尽了其他三个值，所以求和只有一项有效值。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
综上
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}=g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{\rho}+g^{\nu\rho}\gamma^{\mu}-g^{\rho\mu}\gamma^{\nu}+i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma^{5}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
讨论
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
两个矩阵的乘积：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}=g^{\mu\nu}-i\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

，元素是
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
三个矩阵的乘积：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}=g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{\rho}+g^{\nu\rho}\gamma^{\mu}-g^{\mu\rho}\gamma^{\nu}+i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma_{5}$
\end_inset

，元素是
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{\rho}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma_{5}$
\end_inset

,
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
四个矩阵的乘积：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\alpha}=g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\alpha}+g^{\nu\rho}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\alpha}-g^{\mu\rho}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\alpha}-i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{5}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma^{\alpha}$
\end_inset

利用上面的公式。元素是
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\alpha}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{5}$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
-i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{5}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma^{\alpha} & =-i\varepsilon_{\phantom{\mu\nu\rho}\sigma}^{\mu\nu\rho}\gamma_{5}\left(g^{\mu\nu}-i\sigma^{\mu\nu}\right)\\
 & =-\varepsilon_{\phantom{\mu\nu\rho}\sigma}^{\mu\nu\rho}\left(\frac{i}{2}\varepsilon^{\sigma\alpha\theta\zeta}\sigma_{\theta\zeta}+ig^{\sigma\alpha}\gamma_{5}\right)\\
 & =\frac{1}{4}\left(\varepsilon_{\phantom{\mu\nu\rho}\sigma}^{\mu\nu\rho}\varepsilon^{\sigma\alpha\theta\zeta}\sigma_{\theta\zeta}+\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\alpha}\gamma_{5}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
含有
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

矩阵的，利用
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}\sigma^{\mu\nu}=\frac{i}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

乘一个矩阵：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{5}=-\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\mu}$
\end_inset

,元素是
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

乘两个矩阵：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}=\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{5}=\frac{1}{2}\gamma^{5}\left(\sigma^{\mu\nu}+g^{\mu\nu}\right)=\frac{1}{2}g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{5}+\frac{i}{4}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

，元素是
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

,
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

乘三个矩阵：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}=\gamma^{5}\left(g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{\rho}+g^{\nu\rho}\gamma^{\mu}-g^{\mu\rho}\gamma^{\nu}+i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma_{5}\right)=g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\rho}+g^{\nu\rho}\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\mu}-g^{\mu\rho}\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\nu}-i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}$
\end_inset

，元素是
\begin_inset Formula $g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\rho}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

乘四个矩阵：
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\alpha}=g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\alpha}+g^{\nu\rho}\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\alpha}-g^{\mu\rho}\gamma^{5}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\alpha}-i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma_{\sigma}\gamma^{\alpha}$
\end_inset

，元素是
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
旋量的表示，洛伦兹群生成元满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left[J_{\mu\nu},J_{\rho\sigma}\right] & =i(g_{\nu\rho}J_{\mu\sigma}-g_{\mu\rho}J_{\nu\sigma}-g_{\nu\sigma}J_{\mu\rho}+g_{\mu\sigma}J_{\nu\rho})
\end{align*}

\end_inset

考虑到
\begin_inset Formula $g_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

是对称张量，指标顺序无所谓，上面可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[J_{12},J_{34}\right]=ig_{\text{rest}}J_{(14+23-24-13)}
\]

\end_inset

rest 表示剩下的指标。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{\mu\nu}=\frac{i}{4}\left[\gamma^{\mu},\gamma^{\nu}\right]
\]

\end_inset

满足这个对易关系，是洛伦兹群生成元的四维旋量表示，所以
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}=\frac{i}{2}\left[\gamma^{\mu},\gamma^{\nu}\right]$
\end_inset

满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left[\sigma_{12},\sigma_{34}\right] & =2ig_{\text{rest}}\sigma_{(14+23-24-13)}\\
 & =2i(g_{23}\sigma_{14}-g_{14}\sigma_{23}-g_{13}\sigma_{24}+g_{24}\sigma_{13})
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
利用
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\mu}=-\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}+2g^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma_{\mu\nu} & =-\frac{2}{4}\left(\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma_{\mu}\gamma_{\nu}-\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma_{\nu}\gamma_{\mu}\right)\\
 & =-\frac{2}{4}\left(\left(-4*4+2*4\right)-4*4\right)\\
 & =\frac{-1}{2}(-8-16)=12\\
\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma_{\mu\nu} & =12
\end{align*}

\end_inset

如同泡利矩阵,
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

矩阵的模为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma_{\mu\nu}=1,\mu\neq\nu$
\end_inset

（重复指标不求和，并注意指标的位置）
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\rho\sigma}=\frac{-2}{4}\left(\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\sigma}-\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\sigma}\gamma^{\rho}\right)
\]

\end_inset

由于
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

是反对称的，所以考虑
\begin_inset Formula $\rho\neq\sigma$
\end_inset

,利用
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}=i\gamma^{0}\gamma^{1}\gamma^{2}\gamma^{3}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\rho\sigma} & =\frac{-4}{4}\left(\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\sigma}\right)=-\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\sigma}\\
 & =i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma^{5}-g^{\mu\nu}\gamma^{\rho}\gamma^{\sigma}-\cdots-g^{\mu\nu}g^{\rho\sigma}-\cdots
\end{align*}

\end_inset

省略号代表各种可能的组合，如果
\begin_inset Formula $\mu,\nu,\rho,\sigma$
\end_inset

各不相等，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\rho\sigma}=i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma^{5}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
所以有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\gamma^{5} & =\frac{-i}{4!}\varepsilon_{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\rho\sigma}=\frac{i}{4!}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\mu\nu}\sigma_{\rho\sigma}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
证明：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}\sigma^{\mu\nu}=\frac{i}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

,利用
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\rho\sigma}=i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

，右边乘上
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{5}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\gamma^{5}\right)^{2}=1$
\end_inset

,注意这些指标
\begin_inset Formula $\mu,\nu,\rho,\sigma$
\end_inset

各不相等
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\rho\sigma}= & i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\gamma^{5}\\
\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\rho\sigma}\gamma^{5}= & i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\\
\sigma_{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\rho\sigma}\gamma^{5}= & i\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\mu\nu}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{\mu\nu}\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

这个求和中的指标跟
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

中的
\begin_inset Formula $\rho\sigma$
\end_inset

不能相等，
\begin_inset Formula $\rho,\sigma$
\end_inset

也不相等，因为指标总数为
\begin_inset Formula $0,1,2,3$
\end_inset

,如此一来，求和只有两项,如
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{12}\sigma^{12}+\sigma_{21}\sigma^{21}=2$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sigma^{\rho\sigma}\gamma^{5} & =\frac{i}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\mu\nu}\text{ 交换指标次序}\\
\gamma^{5}\sigma^{\rho\sigma} & =\frac{i}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}\sigma_{\rho\sigma}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Dirac 表示
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Dirac 表示可有 Wyel 表示做一个 幺正变换得到
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma_{D}=\mathcal{U}^{\dagger}\gamma_{w}\mathcal{U},\quad\mathcal{U}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & 1\\
1 & -1
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

Dirac 矩阵的形式为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma^{0}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & 0\\
0 & -1
\end{array}\right),\quad\vec{\gamma}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & \vec{\sigma}\\
-\vec{\sigma} & 0
\end{array}\right)\quad\gamma^{5}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & 1\\
1 & 0
\end{array}\right),\quad C=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & -i\sigma_{2}\\
-i\sigma_{2} & 0
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
自旋–
\begin_inset Formula $1/2$
\end_inset

旋量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Dirac 方程平面波解的振幅部分(旋量部分),
\begin_inset Formula $\psi=u\exp\left(-ip\cdot x\right)+v\exp(ip\cdot x)$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\slashed{p}-m\right)u(p)=0
\]

\end_inset

使用Dirac表象中的 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

 矩阵，Dirac双旋量可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{\lambda}(p)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+m}w_{\lambda}\\
\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}-m}\left(\vec{n}\cdot\vec{\sigma}\right)w_{\lambda}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

它定义了一个粒子，能量是
\begin_inset Formula $E_{\vec{p}}$
\end_inset

，动量为
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}$
\end_inset

,沿着单位矢量
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{n}\equiv\vec{p}/\sqrt{\vec{p}^{2}}$
\end_inset

的方向运动。Weyl 旋量
\begin_inset Formula $w_{\lambda}$
\end_inset

是螺旋度算符的本征函数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
回忆起 Pauli-Lubanski 矢量为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W^{\mu}=\frac{1}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}P_{\nu}M_{\rho\sigma}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
求解：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在这个坐标系中，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\slashed{p}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
E_{\vec{p}} & -\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\\
\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma} & -E_{\vec{p}}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

所以，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\slashed{p}-m=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
E_{\vec{p}}-m & -\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\\
\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma} & -E_{\vec{p}}-m
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

令
\begin_inset Formula $u(p)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
w_{1}\\
w_{2}
\end{array}\right)$
\end_inset

，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
\left(E_{\vec{p}}-m\right)w_{1}-\left(\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)w_{2}=0\\
\left(\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)w_{1}-\left(E_{\vec{p}}+m\right)w_{2}=0
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

考虑到
\begin_inset Formula $E^{2}-p^{2}=m^{2}$
\end_inset

，以及
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \sigma^{i},\sigma^{j}\right\} =2\delta^{ij},\left(\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)^{2}=p^{i}\sigma^{i}p^{j}\sigma^{j}=p^{2}$
\end_inset

。这两个方程是等价的。化简为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
w_{2}=\frac{\left(\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)}{E_{\vec{p}}+m}w_{1}
\]

\end_inset

重新选择归一化，令
\begin_inset Formula $w_{1}=\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+m}w_{\lambda}$
\end_inset

，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
w_{2} & =\frac{\left(\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+m}}{E_{\vec{p}}+m}w_{\lambda}=\frac{\left(\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}-m}}{\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+m}\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}-m}}w_{\lambda}\\
 & =\frac{\left(\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}-m}}{\sqrt{\vec{p}^{2}}}w_{\lambda}=\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}-m}\left(\vec{n}\cdot\vec{\sigma}\right)w_{\lambda}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\color red
最终得到
\color inherit
，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{\lambda}(p)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+m}w_{\lambda}\\
\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}-m}\left(\vec{n}\cdot\vec{\sigma}\right)w_{\lambda}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
其中
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{n}\equiv\vec{p}/\sqrt{\vec{p}^{2}}$
\end_inset

，为动量方向的单位矢量。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{0}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & 0\\
0 & -1
\end{array}\right)$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{u}=u^{\dagger}\gamma^{0}=(u_{1}^{\dagger},-u_{2}^{\dagger})$
\end_inset

,归一化为,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{u}_{\lambda}(p)u_{\lambda^{\prime}}(p)=\left(E_{\vec{p}}+m\right)-\left(E_{\vec{p}}-m\right)\delta_{\lambda\lambda^{\prime}}=2m\delta_{\lambda\lambda^{\prime}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\color red
同理，在Weyl表象下,
\color inherit

\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\slashed{p}-m=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
-m & E_{\vec{p}}-\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\\
E_{\vec{p}}+\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma} & -m
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

令
\begin_inset Formula $u(p)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
w_{1}\\
w_{2}
\end{array}\right)$
\end_inset

，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
\left(-m\right)w_{1}+\left(E_{\vec{p}}-\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)w_{2}=0\\
\left(E_{\vec{p}}+\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)w_{1}+\left(-m\right)w_{2}=0
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

同上，这两个方程是等价的，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
w_{1}=\frac{\left(E_{\vec{p}}-\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)}{m}w_{2}
\]

\end_inset

重新选择归一化，令
\begin_inset Formula $w_{2}=\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}}w_{\lambda}$
\end_inset

，得到,
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
w_{1}=\frac{m}{\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}}}w_{\lambda}
\]

\end_inset

这里
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{}$
\end_inset

的含义应该理解为，变换到对角表象中开方后再逆变换回来。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\color red
最终得到
\color inherit
，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{\lambda}(p)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
\frac{m}{\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}}}w_{\lambda}\\
\sqrt{E_{\vec{p}}+\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}}w_{\lambda}
\end{array}\right)=\sqrt{m}\left(\begin{array}{c}
bw_{\lambda}\\
b^{-1}w_{\lambda}
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $b=\sqrt{\left(E_{\vec{p}}-\vec{p}.\vec{\sigma}\right)/m}=\sqrt{p.\sigma/m}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset


\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\xout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
\color none
在静止系为
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

。将
\family default
\series default
\shape default
\size default
\emph default
\bar default
\strikeout default
\xout default
\uuline default
\uwave default
\noun default
\color inherit

\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

称为
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

在动量方向投影的根，简称
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

投影根。 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
顺便一提，
\begin_inset Formula $b^{-1}(p^{\mu})=b(-p^{\mu})$
\end_inset

，也就是说，动量反向，矩阵变成逆矩阵。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{0}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
0 & 1\\
1 & 0
\end{array}\right)$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{u}=u^{\dagger}\gamma^{0}=(u_{2}^{\dagger},u_{1}^{\dagger})$
\end_inset

,归一化为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\bar{u}_{\lambda}(p)u_{\lambda^{\prime}}(p)=mw_{\lambda}^{\dagger}w_{\lambda^{\prime}}+mw_{\lambda}^{\dagger}w_{\lambda^{\prime}}=2m\delta_{\lambda\lambda^{\prime}}
\]

\end_inset

我们看到，每一项的来源都很清晰，
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

来自于
\begin_inset Formula $u_{\lambda}(p)$
\end_inset

中包含两个基础旋量，
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

来自于旋量解外面的系数
\begin_inset Formula $\sqrt{m}$
\end_inset

，内部的
\begin_inset Formula $b,b^{-1}$
\end_inset

来自于
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{0}$
\end_inset

作用后，归一化 cancel 的要求。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果是负能解
\begin_inset Formula $\psi=u\exp\left(-ip\cdot x\right)+v\exp(ip\cdot x)$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\slashed{p}-m\right)u(p)=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
补充 Pauli-Lubanski
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
回忆起 Pauli-Lubanski 矢量为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W^{\mu}=\frac{1}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}P_{\nu}M_{\rho\sigma}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $M_{\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $SO(3,1)$
\end_inset

生成元。最一般的形式为
\begin_inset Formula $M_{\mu\nu}=L_{\mu\nu}+S_{\mu\nu}=i(x_{\mu}\partial_{\nu}-x_{\nu}\partial_{\mu})+S_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Formula $S_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

厄米，对
\begin_inset Formula $\mu\nu$
\end_inset

反对称，满足和
\begin_inset Formula $L_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

同样的李代数，并且与
\begin_inset Formula $L_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

对易。也就是分别作用在函数上和旋量上。一般的表示可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{c}
\psi_{1}(x)\\
\psi_{2}(x)\\
\vdots\\
\psi_{n}(x)
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset

函数和旋量结构在洛伦兹群作用下，都要进行相应的变换。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $P_{\mu}=i\partial_{\mu}=i\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\mu}}$
\end_inset

是厄米的时空平移生成元。
\begin_inset Formula $\left[M_{\mu\nu},P_{\rho}\right]=-ig_{\mu\rho}P_{\nu}+ig_{\nu\rho}P_{\mu}$
\end_inset

，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W^{\mu}=-\frac{i}{2}\varepsilon^{\mu\nu\rho\sigma}S_{\rho\sigma}\partial_{\nu}
\]

\end_inset

由此可见，
\begin_inset Formula $W^{\mu}$
\end_inset

实际上只和洛伦兹生成元中的“自旋”部分
\begin_inset Formula $S_{\rho\sigma}$
\end_inset

有关。
\end_layout

